description:
Are you ready for the coming storm? Are you prepared to meet it with the sword of God? 

This #short video from Pastor Ted Wilsons weekly message reminds us that, in order to prepare and be ready for the coming storm, we should take on the sword of God, as Ephesians 6:17 says, And take the helmet of salvation, and the sword of the Spirit, which is the word of God.

Listen to Pastor Ted Wilsons message reminding us to be ready for the storm, taking up the sword of the Lord to be victorious.  https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o6auLZNEAsg&list=PL-k2Gb-DBYo_ANrUJhHN2_4bSlMDTjuqQ&index=69
